it.csi.mddtools.guigen
Interface JumpCommand

All Superinterfaces:
Command, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
public interface JumpCommand
extends Command

A representation of the model object 'Jump Command'. Permette di passare alla visualizzazione di un ContentPanel differente.

The following features are supported:

  • Jump To
  • Push Current Page

See Also:
